<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/30773177">历史上有哪些有名的妹控？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4491588" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">Cesare Borgia，姜诸儿这些著名德骨病友自不必说……想知道还有哪些。</div>


</div>
